<p>In case you&#39;re still uncertain - maybe time has passed since I wrote this and you&#39;re wondering if something has changed - the <a href="https://help.openai.com/en/articles/6825453-chatgpt-release-notes" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">ChatGPT release notes</a> should definitely include news of a monumental change like the ability to fetch content from the web.</p>